Package model.map

Class MapListing

java.lang.Object
model.map.MapGraph
model.map.MapDetailAccess
model.map.MapListing
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class MapListing
extends MapDetailAccess
This class is to get some lists and correspondence from the model.map file Including: the continent list, the total country list , the country list from a continent and the list of neighbour countries.
